<plot>Buenos Aires. It rains. Alma is in her car, stuck in Buenos Aires' traffic. She have been living in her little car since her boyfriend left her. Suddenly, Roberto gets into the car. He's wet and hurt , he's tired of the rain, of broken dreams. He have came back after thirty years abroad. In this new city he has nothing and nobody, just a father in coma, whom he has no relationship. He promises to leave the car as soon as the rain ceases. Alma, not knowing exactly why lets him in. That night will be different. And the next few days too. There's something new to find in the depth of their hearts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?339675</url></doc>
